## Mod Features:
- Real-time Pal stat overlay
- Hidden stat revelation
- Breeding compatibility checker
- Combat effectiveness ratings
- Customizable UI positioning
- Performance optimized

## Installation:
1. Extract to Palworld installation directory
2. Ensure PalSchema is installed
3. Launch Palworld and press F8 to configure